CatDescriptText: Related article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 20, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "...Clyde O. Davis has done same [applied for marriage license] in order to make his Mrs. Julia Tyner of Atlantic City, N. J. ..."
TitMainTitle: Groom, possibly Clyde Davis wearing dark three piece suit, and bride, possibly Julia Tyner Davis wearing dark suit, large corsage, and light colored crocheted blouse, posed in interior with woven curtains and striped wallpaper
